'''格力·安東尼·羅拔·馬卡爾-史密夫'''（{{lang-en|'''Craig Anthony Robert Mackail-Smith'''}}，{{bd|1984年|2月25日|catidx=Mackail-Smith, Craig}}）是一名[[英格蘭|英格蘭]][[足球|足球]][[運動員|運動員]]，司職[[前鋒_(足球)|前鋒]]，現時效力於[[英格蘭足球冠軍聯賽|英冠]]的[[布莱顿足球俱乐部|白禮頓]]。他亦曾代表當時稱為「英格蘭半職業代表隊」（''England semi-professional team''）的[[英格蘭足球代表丙隊|英格蘭C隊]]參加國際賽，於7場上陣射入4球<ref name="englandc">{{cite news |language=en |title=England take the trophy |url=http://www.thefa.com/England/NationalGameXI/NewsAndFeatures/Postings/2006/11/EnglandNGXI_vHolland.htm |publisher=[[英格蘭足球總會|''thefa.com'']] |date=2006-11-29 |accessdate=2008-12-30 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20080720013150/http://www.thefa.com/England/NationalGameXI/NewsAndFeatures/Postings/2006/11/EnglandNGXI_vHolland.htm |archivedate=2008-07-20 }}</ref>，於2011年轉籍代表[[蘇格蘭足球代表隊|蘇格蘭]]參賽。

==生平==
===球會===
馬卡爾-史密夫出身[[聖奧爾本斯城足球會|聖奧爾本斯城]]青訓系統，惟一直表現平平，於30場正選及15場後補上陣僅取得兩個入球，於2003年遭球會放棄。

2007年1月29日[[彼得伯勒联足球俱乐部|彼德堡]]從[[英格蘭足球議會全國聯賽|全國聯]]領頭羊[[达根汉姆和雷德布里奇足球俱乐部|杜根咸]]簽入馬卡爾-史密夫，轉會費沒有透露，簽約兩年半<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11756_2403749,00.html |title=Posh acquire Daggers |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2007-01-29 |accessdate=2010-12-23 |archive-date=2008-10-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081011161615/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11756_2403749,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但他因私人問題延後一週才向新球會報到，惹起一場小風波<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11764_2404670,00.html |title=Posh new boy makes amends |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2007-02-05 |accessdate=2010-12-23 |archive-date=2008-09-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080907131043/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11764_2404670,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。同期加入的還有同樣來自非聯賽球會的[[阿隆·麦克林|阿隆·麦克林]]（[[格雷斯竞技足球俱乐部|格雷斯]]）和[[乔治·博伊德|乔治·博伊德]]（[[史提芬納治足球會|-{zh-hans:保罗夫史提芬; zh-hk:史提芬納治;}-]]），三人組成的鋒線協助球隊成功連續兩年升班到[[英冠|英冠]]。

2008年3月17日馬卡爾-史密夫與彼德堡續簽新約留隊至2012年<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11750_3316932,00.html |title=New deal for Posh striker |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2008-03-17 |accessdate=2010-12-23 |archive-date=2016-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308010948/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11750_3316932,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在球會升班[[英甲|英甲]]後，馬卡爾-史密夫的出色表現吸引[[卡迪夫城足球俱乐部|卡迪夫城]]及[[伯明翰足球會|伯明翰城]]的注意，但彼德堡拒絕出售陣中主力球員以爭取升班<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11688_4327619,00.html |title=Posh issue hands-off warning |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2008-10-13 |accessdate=2010-12-23 |archive-date=2016-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310085529/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11688_4327619,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2009年1月據報[[蘇超|蘇超]]球會[[凯尔特人足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:凯尔特人; zh-hk:些路迪;}-]]有意一併購入馬卡爾-史密夫、阿隆·麦克林及乔治·博伊德，但彼德堡管理層開出每名球員500萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]的天價<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11719_4835746,00.html |title=Fry - Posh trio will cost £15m |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2009-01-23 |accessdate=2010-12-23 |archive-date=2016-03-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160309135501/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11719_4835746,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2011年3月15日，彼德堡拒絕[[英冠|英冠]]球會[[诺里奇城足球俱乐部|诺里奇城]]對馬卡爾-史密夫的出價<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/peterborough_united/9425263.stm |title=Peterborough reject bid from Norwich for Mackail-Smith |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-03-15 |accessdate=2011-03-21 |archive-date=2017-02-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170217150740/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/peterborough_united/9425263.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，諾域治表示早前已基本達成轉會費金額協議，但商討中途彼德堡卻要求加價，將馬卡爾-史密夫的身價訂為200萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]另加100萬英鎊附加條款<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/n/norwich/9428228.stm |title=McNally accuses Peterborough of raising fee for striker |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-03-17 |accessdate=2011-03-21 |archive-date=2017-02-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170217150733/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/n/norwich/9428228.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。3月20日馬卡爾-史密夫獲選「英甲年度最佳球員」<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/9431137.stm |title=QPR's Adel Taarabt wins Football League player of year |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-03-21 |accessdate=2011-03-21 |archive-date=2017-08-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170827175838/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_1/9431137.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。5月29日馬卡爾-史密夫在升班附加賽決賽射入1球，協助彼德堡以3-0擊敗[[哈德斯菲尔德足球俱乐部|哈德斯菲爾德]]及取得最後一張[[英冠|英冠]]入場劵<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/13489373.stm |title=Huddersfield 0-3 Peterborough |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-05-29 |accessdate=2011-07-13 |archive-date=2011-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111109005713/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/13489373.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，而他在彼德堡的入球總數亦達到99球。

球季結束後彼德堡隨即宣佈接納一支[[英超|英超]]球隊對馬卡爾-史密夫的出價<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/13605335.stm |title=Peterborough United accept Craig Mackail-Smith offer |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-06-01 |accessdate=2011-07-13 |archive-date=2011-06-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110603095707/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/13605335.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，其後主席[[達瑞·麦安东尼|達瑞·麦安东尼]]（Darragh MacAnthony）又在[[Twitter|Twitter]]上說傳聞中的[[威根竞技足球俱乐部|韋根]]並未有出價<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/13731831.stm |title='No Wigan bid' for Craig Mackail-Smith say Peterborough |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-06-10 |accessdate=2011-07-13 |archive-date=2011-08-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110812005411/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/13731831.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2011年6月27日球會又發佈消息指已同意[[莱斯特城足球俱乐部|莱斯特城]]的出價，並表示[[西汉姆联足球俱乐部|韋斯咸]]亦有意競逐，而馬卡爾-史密夫已拒絕兩支升班馬[[诺里奇城足球俱乐部|诺里奇城]]及[[女王公园巡游者足球俱乐部|昆士柏流浪]]的邀請<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/13933976.stm |title=Peterborough agree Leicester Craig Mackail-Smith bid |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-06-27 |accessdate=2011-07-13 |archive-date=2011-07-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110702140625/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/13933976.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。7月4日新升[[英冠|英冠]]的[[布莱顿足球俱乐部|白禮頓]]遲來先上岸，與馬卡爾-史密夫正式簽署四年合約，轉會費金額沒有透露<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/13991715.stm |title=Craig Mackail-Smith heads to Brighton in four-year deal |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-07-04 |accessdate=2011-07-13 |archive-date=2011-09-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110907133730/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/13991715.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===國家隊===
雖然馬卡爾-史密夫在[[英格蘭|英格蘭]]出生及長大，並曾代表[[英格蘭足球代表丙隊|英格蘭C隊]]上陣達到7場，但他仍可以其[[祖母|祖母]]瑪嘉烈的祖籍代表[[蘇格蘭足球代表隊|蘇格蘭]]，而他亦表示如獲徵召將有興趣追隨隊友[[乔治·博伊德|乔治·博伊德]]代表蘇格蘭參賽<ref name="Mackail-Smith keen to follow Boyd to Scotland">{{cite news |language=en |title=Mackail Smith keen to follow Boyd to Scotland |url=http://www.peterboroughtoday.co.uk/sport/mackail_smith_keen_to_follow_boyd_to_scotland_1_130607 |publisher=''peterboroughtoday.co.uk'' |date=2009-05-05 |accessdate=2010-12-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121003054208/http://www.peterboroughtoday.co.uk/sport/mackail_smith_keen_to_follow_boyd_to_scotland_1_130607 |archive-date=2012-10-03 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。2011年3月27日他首次代表[[蘇格蘭足球代表隊|蘇格蘭]]在[[倫敦|倫敦]][[酋長球場|酋長球場]]對[[巴西國家足球隊|巴西]]的[[友誼賽|友誼賽]]上陣<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/scotland/9431234.stm |title=Scotland 0-2 Brazil |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-03-27 |accessdate=2011-03-28 |archive-date=2020-08-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200803094834/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/scotland/9431234.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

